
####  MOUSE-BINDINGS

##  Bindings for mouse left-click on titlebar buttons [M1]
##
##      T/button 1                            Windows-Tools-Menu
##      T/button 2                            Close Window
##      T/button 4                            Maximize/Restore
##      T/button 6                            Iconify
##
##  Bindings for mouse roller-ball in titlebar [M2]
##
##      Roll up                               WindowShade On
##      Roll down                             WindowShade Off
##
##  Bindings for mouse right-click [M3]
##
##      In Root Window                        Open Root-Tools-Menu
##      In Window Frame/Sides/Titlebar        Open Windows-Tools-Menu
##      Double right-click in titlebar        Toggle Shade
##
##  Bindings for left-click [M4]
##
##      In Root Window                        Open Main-Menu
##      On Iconified Window                   DeIconify
##

####  KEY-BINDINGS

##  * Miscellaneous [K1]
##
##      Win-S                                Toggle Statusbar
##      Win-C                                Clipboard Menu
##      Win-G                                gmrun
##
##  * Menus bindings [K2]
##
##      Ctrl-Esc                             Main-Menu
##      Win-Esc                              Root-Tools-Menu
##      Alt-F8                               Windows-Tools-Menu
##
##  * Switch focus to another window [K3]
##
##      Alt-Tab                              Focus Next Non-Iconic 
##      Win-Tab                              Focus Next Iconic 
##
##  * Basic window operations [K4]
##
##      Alt-F11                              Maximize
##      Alt-F10                              Restore/Maximize
##      Alt-F9                               Iconify 
##      Alt-F5                               Center 
##      Alt-F4                               Close 
##      Win-U/D/L/R                          Move 
##      Alt-Win-U/D/L/R                      Resize 
##
##         * U/D/L/R == up/down/left/right cursor keys
##
##  * Zoom/Shrink the current window (urxvt only) [K5]
##
##      Ctl-Win - Left/Right                 Horizontal only
##      Ctl-Win - Up/Down                    Vertical only
##      Alt     - Up/Down                    Vert. + Horiz.
##
##  * Switch to another workspace [K6]
##
##      Shift-Win - 1-9                      shift window to wkspc $num
##      Shift-Win - Left/Right               shift window to L/R wkspc
##      Win       - 1-9                      shift user to wkspc $num
##      Alt       - Left/Right               shift user to L/R wkspc
##
##  * Volume + Brightness (as well as multimedia keys)  [K7]
##    
##      Win-F1                               Volume down
##      Win-F2                               Volume up
##      Win-F3                               Brightness down
##      Win-F4                               Brightness up
##      Win-F5                               Contrast down
##      Win-F6                               Contrast up
##    


















